We buy houses in a variety of situations: - Inherited property / probate - Divorce - Major repairs needed - Foreclosure / forbearance - Problem tenants - Need to sell immediately We can buy even if the home is in foreclosure or close to it, and even if there are tenants living in it. Please visit our website or contact us through LinkedIn to arrange a free, no-obligation consultation by phone or videoconference. We look forward to helping you sell your home fast!
